sub_fields.label: iframe
sub_fields.name: iframe
sub_fields.instructions: Paste only your iframe URL into this field.

sub_fields.label: Heading
sub_fields.name: heading
sub_fields.instructions: This is the headline which will display at the top of the section.

sub_fields.label: Sub-heading
sub_fields.name: sub-heading
sub_fields.instructions: This text will display under the main heading.

sub_fields.label: Slide Image
sub_fields.name: slide_image
sub_fields.instructions: This is the image which will appear as one half of the slide.

sub_fields.label: Slide Title
sub_fields.name: slide_title
sub_fields.instructions: This text will appear above the main slide text.

sub_fields.label: Slide Content
sub_fields.name: slide_content
sub_fields.instructions: This is the main text-body of the slide.

sub_fields.label: Button 1
sub_fields.name: button_1
sub_fields.instructions: Create a button with a a URL link.

sub_fields.label: Button 2
sub_fields.name: button_2
sub_fields.instructions: Create another button with a URL link.

sub_fields.label: Header
sub_fields.name: arrow_header
sub_fields.instructions: This will be the header for the Arrow-Tile section.

sub_fields.label: Sub Header
sub_fields.name: arrow_sub_header
sub_fields.instructions: This text will go below the header and above the arrow tiles.

sub_fields.label: Tile Image
sub_fields.name: tile_image
sub_fields.instructions: This is the svg displayed in the tile.

sub_fields.label: Tile Text
sub_fields.name: tile_text
sub_fields.instructions: This text will appear in the tile. Brevity is encouraged.

sub_fields.label: Background Color
sub_fields.name: background_color
sub_fields.instructions: Chose a background color for your announcement bar. Orange is default.

sub_fields.label: Text Color
sub_fields.name: text_color
sub_fields.instructions: Choose the color of your announcement text. White is default.

sub_fields.label: Announcement URL
sub_fields.name: url
sub_fields.instructions: The URL you would like the announcement bar to link to.

sub_fields.label: Instructions
sub_fields.message: We're including this form from HubSpot. Edit it there and it'll be updated here (and on every page this module appears).

sub_fields.label: Hubspot Form ID
sub_fields.name: hubspot_form_id
sub_fields.instructions: Enter the name of the HubSpot form which will be filled out by this quiz.

sub_fields.label: Stat Name
sub_fields.name: name
sub_fields.instructions: Choose a short name to identify this stat. ex: companies, man_hours, etc.

sub_fields.label: Data Path
sub_fields.name: data_path
sub_fields.instructions: This is the path used to retrieve your data point, which should look like a URL. The value retrieved will display as the large statistic number.
